            &lt;h1 id=&#34;ffmpeg--whisper-audio-transcription-and-subtitle-extraction&#34;&gt;FFmpeg + Whisper: Audio Transcription and Subtitle Extraction&lt;/h1&gt;
&lt;h2 id=&#34;overview&#34;&gt;Overview&lt;/h2&gt;
&lt;p&gt;This guide covers how to use FFmpeg in combination with OpenAI&#39;s Whisper to extract transcriptions and generate subtitles from audio and video files. FFmpeg handles media processing while Whisper provides state-of-the-art speech recognition.&lt;/p&gt;
